divs: Sighting Detailsit was a friday around 12 whin i decide to have lunch i boiled pasta and took it in my backyard to eat whin i walked out i had an eary feeling that something was watching me and there was a strong sulfur like smell in the air whin i noticed the craft it was over the nabors house less than ten feet off the ground and it was spining in a clockwise motion it slowley loomed over my property line and my dog started barcking i saw a black shiny object fall off craft and land in my pool i havent removed it for research purposes . after it droped the object the craft started spinning upword extreamly fast i ran to get my camera but it was gone before i got back there was also a large tar like stain under where the craft was hovering it stank of chloride and killed the grass i have that section of my yard blocked off until u get here please come i have physical evidince in my pool and stains on my grass and i am very fasinated to findout what your take on it is. sicerley jim
